<html style="overflow: auto!important;">

  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/{{mode}}.css">   
    <script src="/assets/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <title>KGSACU CP</title>
    <style>
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="p-3 h-100 w-100 container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
          <p>Use this page to edit the Admin Returns and Serials that will be used for the Record Transmission feature. This
              should be done upon updates of the Signalling Operation Instruction.</p>
          <p>Use the pane on the right to add, remove or edit Admin Returns. Then select "Edit Serials" in order to change
              serials. A table will appear in place of this window.</p>
          <p>Use the "Add Serial" Button to create rows in the table and then edit them with the Serial, the Description, the
              Data Type (see below) and Options (see below).</p>
          <p>There are 4 Data Types:</p>
          <table class="table table-borderless">
            <tr>
              <td class="bold">short</td>
              <td><input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" autocomplete="off"/></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="bold">long</td>
              <td><textarea class="form-control form-control-sm" rows="3" cols="40"></textarea></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="bold">location</td>
              <td><input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" list="locs" autocomplete="off"/>
                <datalist id="locs">
                  {{#each locations}}
                    <option value="{{this}}">
                  {{/each}}
                </datalist>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="bold">option</td>              
              <td>
                <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                  <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="inlineRadioOptions" id="inlineRadio1" value="option1">
                  <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio1">Option 1</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                  <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="inlineRadioOptions" id="inlineRadio2" value="option2">
                  <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio2">Option 2</label>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <p>For the option data type, use the option column to declare the options, seperated by a comma and space.</p>
          <p><b>This will synchronize across the server, so must only be changed on one laptop.</b></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <table class="table align-middle">
            <thead>
              <th>Returns</th>
              <th>Options</th>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="transmissions-table">
              {{#each transmissions}}
                <tr class="transmission-row">
                  <td>{{this}}</td>
                  <td>
                    <button class="btn btn-sm theme-button edit-return">Edit</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-sm theme-button delete-return">Delete</button>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              {{/each}}
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <button id="new-return" class="btn btn-sm theme-button">New Return</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade" id="serials-modal" tabindex="-1">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl modal-dialog-centered modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <form action="none" id="validity-form" autocomplete="off">
            <div class="modal-header">
              <h5 class="modal-title p-2" id="transmission-name">Transmission Name</h5>
              <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <table class="table align-middle">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th style="width:10%">Serial</th>
                    <th>Description</th>
                    <th>Type</th>
                    <th>Options</th>
                    <th>Controls</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody id="serials-tbody" class="">

                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer d-flex">
              <div id="row-buttons" class="align-self-start" style="display:none">
                <button type="button" id="serial-up" class="btn btn-secondary">&#8593;</button>
                <button type="button" id="serial-down" class="btn btn-secondary">&#8595;</button>
                <button type="button" id="delete-serial" class="btn btn-secondary">Delete Serial</button>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-grow-1"></div>
              <div class="align-self-end">
                <button type="button" id="add-serial" class="btn btn-secondary">Add Serial</button>
                <button type="button" id="edit-name" class="btn btn-secondary">Edit Name</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
                <button type="submit" id="save-return" class="btn btn-primary">Save</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/assets/js/helpers.js"></script>
    <script src="/assets/js/settings/serials.js"></script>
    <script src="/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>